Spider-Man stays in the MCU: Another Marvel movie planned
It was a shock for all Spider-Man fans: at the end of August it became known that Sony and Marvel would go their separate ways in the future. Tom Holland's Spider-Man would therefore no longer be part of the " Avengers " universe. It was completely unclear how the films about Tom Holland would continue.
